videos.headline: Rutgers lineman punches QB in the face after TD toss
videos.description: Artur Sitkowski finds Raheem Blackshear for a 74-yard touchdown, then a Rutgers lineman takes a swing at his quarterback to celebrate.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rutgers lineman punches QB in the face after TD toss) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: BC takes early lead with 42-yard TD run
videos.description: David Bailey breaks through Rutgers' defense for a 42-yard score on Boston College's first drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC takes early lead with 42-yard TD run) 2019/09/21 ESHEET
